data.description: Discover your dream home in this spacious 3-bedroom, 2-bath, 1496 sqft haven waiting for a touch of TLC to restore its timeless charm. Nestled just minutes from the convenience of I-85 and I-285, this gem offers easy access to bustling shopping centers, vibrant fitness hubs, and the bustling Atlanta airport. Embrace the potential to craft your ideal living space, where every corner reflects your unique style and vision. With its generous dimensions and prime location, this home presents a canvas for endless possibilities. Whether youCOre seeking a tranquil retreat or a vibrant hub for entertaining, this property promises the lifestyle youCOve been dreaming of. DonCOt miss out on this opportunity to reimagine and revitalize this home into your personal sanctuary in a thriving neighborhood NOTE: Principals of the seller may share ownership in a licensed real estate brokerage. Buyer offered $1000 credit at closing with the use of the seller's preferred lender!
